text: Malagasy Wikipedia is the Malagasy language edition of Wikipedia. Malagasy is an austronesian language mostly spoken in Madagascar as the first language. It is also the national language of Madagascar. ==Articles== Total number of articles written in Malagasy Wikipedia is 82000+. ==Administrators== This wikipedia has 3 administrators along with 13,423 registered users and 42 active users. == Other websites == * Malagasy Wikipedia Category:Wikipedias
title: Malagasy Wikipedia
